sentences: Atsushi Kamijo (上條淳士, Kamijō Atsushi, born March 12, 1963 in Tokyo, Japan) is a Japanese manga artist.
Atsushi made his debut in a special issue of Shonen Sunday in 1983 with the story "Mob Hunter".
